# Frontend (Pak Buddy)

- Stack: React 19, react-scripts/craco, Tailwind 3, Radix/shadcn in `frontend/src/components/ui/`.
- Landing sections live in `frontend/src/App.js`; section components in `frontend/src/components/sections/`.
- Typography: Playfair Display, Archivo Black, Inter, Space Mono (see `index.css`).
- Brand palette: blues and greys from Floor Lord logo.
- Use existing `cn()` from `frontend/src/lib/utils.js` for class merging.
- Blog strip: `BlogStrip.jsx`; posts built from `content/blog/*.md`.

When adding UI, reuse shadcn primitives under `components/ui/` rather than new one-off styles.
